title: Olympic Channel Podcast with Noriaki Kasai, Yun Sung-Bin and Kjetil Jansrud
description: Three legends for episode 13: one Iron Man with a gold medal in skeleton for South Korea, a skiing phenomenon with five Olympic medals and a daredevil ski jumper who is still rubbing shoulders with the young guns in his mid-40s.
